item.title: Prayer bpn6852 in Canadian Indigenous
item.description: *(Na Ité ithui, ethui ninghinta sothan eyínjyái Hutsha-dun, itsua, iney, imiua, ijya: Blessed is the Spot Ninghinta Sothan Jaül Ninghinta sothan jaül, na ku, na jaül, na kashee, Na etsi, na dhawe, so-aji, nund ninachi, Na unclout, na nünd, mun sa’cho, chui, tl’ok caüa Jáüa úzhi Ilé ilsi, Ilé uhuaná sulhan. (Source category: Northern Tutchone) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 6852)
